<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><span class="icon purple"><i class="psicon-upload"></i></span></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Click on this button to upload your own store icon.
The symbol will be displayed in the online store instead of the back end icon.<br>
Available image formats: <strong>PNG</strong>, <strong>JPG</strong> and <strong>GIF</strong>. Ideal image size: <strong>16 x 16 pixels</strong>.</p></td>
</tr>
